    let productdesc = "Looking to transport your yarn without a snag? The Shuert Yarn-Pak delivers proven performance again and again.<br><br>Thousands of tubes and cones of yarn are shipped globally every year for the Textile and Apparel Industry. Getting these fragile items from one place to another without a snag is a challenge. Since its introduction nearly 20 years ago, the Original Shuert Yarn-Pak has delivered a proven solution for the safe and efficient transport of yarn. The Shuert Yarn-Pak features a custom engineered pallet coupled with separators that combine to form a grid pattern structure that cradles and protects tubes and cones of yarn. <br><br>Shuert Yarn-Paks are capable of delivering hundreds of trips without replacement. Not only does the molded design keep the yarn more secure and easier to handle, the pallets are stackable for greater space efficiencies during shipping. Furthermore, after they are emptied, the Yarn-Paks nest smoothly to save space on their return shipments.  The Shuert Yarn-Pak sets the standard for high quality and structural integrity…and that’s why they perform so flawlessly."
